    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "No that won't work because this need to be set for each query with the query.\nSo if I search for \"Iphone 6 case\" optionnalWords will be \"Iphone 6 case\"\nif I search \"Iphone 5 charger\" optionnalWords will be \"Iphone 5 charger\"\n",
